data.value:
Set in Sharm El Sheikh, 1.9 km from Reef Beach, Regency Lodge Hotel offers accommodation with a garden, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi. The hotel features an indoor pool, entertainment staff and an ATM.
At the hotel all rooms have air conditioning, a wardrobe, a balcony with pool view, a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV, bed linen and towels. Each room is equipped with a safety deposit box and some rooms also offer lake views.
A buffet, à la carte or continental breakfast is available every morning at the property.
